subtitle: think of your body of Consciousness like
your home if you are allowing someone or
something to come inside then it can
affect you for good or for ill when it
is for ill people are often so affected
by the energies they let in that they
become depressed or go into a state of
numbness this energy coming in can also
be called a psychic attack the best way
to protect oneself from Psychic attack
is to not react but respond even if you
have negative energies inside and become
low you can always gain confidence and
purification through meditation even if
you have been spiritually Paralyzed by a
psychic attack or unwanted negative
energies you can always jump back on
track it can be difficult to always
respond instead of react because human
nature is driven by emotions especially
the negative ones the ultimate cure to
this is practice the more we practice
forgiveness and responding to situations
the more clarity we receive
